quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  62,9,"ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, 'iidha nada almwdhn lilsalat fi yawm aljmet, famdu 'iilaa smae alkhtbt wa'ada' alslat, watrku albye, wkdhlk alshira' wjmye ma yashghalukm enha, dhlk aldhy 'umrtm bih khayr lkm; lamaa fih min ghfran dhunubikum wmthwbt allah lkm, 'iin kuntum taelamun masalih 'anfusakum fafealuu dhalik. wafi alayat dalil ealaa wjwb hudur aljumeat wastmae alkhtbt"
  62,10,"f'idha samietum alkhtbt, waddaytm alslat, fantashiruu fi alard, watlbu min rizq allah bseykm, wadhkuruu allah kthyrana fi jmye ahwalkm; laealakum tfwzwn bkhyry aldunya walakhrt"
  62,11,"'iidha ra'aa bed almuslimin tijaratan 'aw shyyana min lahu aldunya wazinatuha tfrraqu 'ilyha, watarakuk -ayha alnby- qaymana ealaa alminbar tkhtb, qul lhm-ayha alnby-: ma eind allah min althawab walneym anfe lakum min allahw wamin altjart, wallh- whdh- khayr man rizq waeta, fatlbu mnh, wastaeinuu btaeth ealaa nyl ma eindah min khayri aldunya walakhrt"